# CODEOWNERS for ClanKit
#
# Every PR automatically requests review from the listed owners.
# Combined with branch-protection rule "Require review from Code Owners"
# (Settings → Branches → master → Require a pull request before merging
# → Require review from Code Owners), no PR can merge without owner approval.
#
# Syntax: <pattern> <owner> [<owner>...]
# Owners can be GitHub usernames (@user) or teams (@org/team).
# More-specific patterns later in this file override earlier patterns.

# Default owner for everything in the repo
*       @XiamiYoung
